OL,3,GCentral, Tayside & Fife
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FA cloudy
OL,6,Fevening with outbreaks of rain, the
OL,7,Frain clearing around midnight to leave
OL,8,Fclear spells and a few showers through
OL,9,Fthe early hours. A touch of frost is
OL,10,Fpossible in sheltered spots as the
OL,11,Foccasionally strong northwesterly
OL,12,Fwinds ease.
OL,13,
OL,14,CMonday:FA few early showers, but for a
OL,15,Fmost a dry day with variable amounts
OL,16,Fof cloud and sunny intervals. The
OL,17,Foccasionally fresh northwesterly
OL,18,Fbreeze continues to ease.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
